casebody.data:
Thursday, December 29, 1994

MOTION DOCKET

94-1640. No. 65596. Regetz v. Cleveland Civ. Serv. Comm. Cuyahoga County,

This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellants’ motion for injunctive relief,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for injunctive relief be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective December 28, 1994.
